    <h1>YOOCHOOSE</h1><div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The external service provider YOOCHOOSE offers an alternative to plentymarkets cross-selling. YOOCHOOSE offers online store customers individually tailored cross-selling recommendations that are based on statistical analyses of the user’s behavior. The YOOCHOOSE Recommender Engine offers personalised product recommendations by combining knowledge about your products with your customers' consumer behavior to give individual recommendations. Recommendations range from the simple Amazon approach of "Customers Who Bought This Item Also Bought" all the way to individually personalized recommendations and recommendations that automatically improve over time.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>YOOCHOOSE offers the following features:</p>
</div>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>Calculating recommendations:</strong>Latest patented algorithms are used to calculate precise recommendations based on a combination of the user’s activity and knowledge of your portfolio.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Situation-based presentation:</strong> The placement as well as the context on both the main pages and detailed pages have an influence on the algorithms and filters that are used.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Optimization with the help of filters:</strong> The use of suitable filters for categories, duplicates, time frames or previously displayed recommendations will greatly improve the quality of recommendations.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Fallback:</strong> If there is no usage or profile data available for a particular item or customer, then fall-back solutions will be used automatically to give suitable recommendations.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Statistical analysis:</strong> Statistical analyses of the solution’s utilization and acceptance.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_registering_with_yoochoose">1. Registering with YOOCHOOSE</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as described below to register with YOOCHOOSE.</p>
</div>
