<h2 id="_setting_up_yoochoose_in_plentymarkets">2. Setting up YOOCHOOSE in plentymarkets</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>After you have entered your YOOCHOOSE registration details, additional tabs are displayed that allow you to set up YOOCHOOSE in plentymarkets.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_configuring_recommendations_and_layout">2.1. Configuring recommendations and layout</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>With the options that you set in this tab, you decide which items should be offered to a customer as cross-selling items. While the options for the category layout provide more general results, the possibilities for the item layout are more specific.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Configuring recommendations and layout:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
